== About me
I am a third-year PhD student at [https://www.inria.fr/en/inria-centre-universite-cote-dazur Inria], France, under the supervision of [http://www-sop.inria.fr/members/Giovanni.Neglia/ Prof. Giovanni Neglia] and [http://www-sop.inria.fr/members/Alain.Jean-Marie/ Prof. Alain Jean-Marie] (Team [https://team.inria.fr/neo/team-members/ NEO]).\n
I received the B.Sc. degree in computer engineering and the M.Sc. degree in Telecommunications from [https://poliba.esse3.cineca.it/Guide/PaginaCorso.do?corso_id=10016 Polytechnic University of Bari], Italy, in 2018 and 2020, respectively.\n
As part of a double diploma program, I also received the M.Sc. degree in computer engineering from [https://ubinet.univ-cotedazur.fr Université Côte D'Azur], France.\n

== Research
My research interests include:
- Distributed optimization for Machine Learning
- Resource-awareness in Federated Learning
- Energy and carbon footprint of ML training

